(70, 'fr', '<h2>Lettre d\'Adhésion</h2><p>Date: {date}</p><p>Cher/Chère <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>Nous sommes heureux de vous accueillir chez {company_name} en tant que {designation}.</p><p>Date d\'Entrée: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Salaire: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Département: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>Nous attendons avec impatience votre précieuse contribution au succès de notre entreprise.</p><p>Cordialement,<br><strong>Département RH</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(71, 'he', '<h2>מכתב הצטרפות</h2><p>תאריך: {date}</p><p><strong>{employee_name}</strong> יקר/ה,</p><p>אנו שמחים לקבל אותך ל-{company_name} בתפקיד {designation}.</p><p>תאריך התחלה: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>משכורת: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>מחלקה: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>אנו מצפים לתרומתך החשובה להצלחת החברה שלנו.</p><p>בברכה,<br><strong>מחלקת משאבי אנוש</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(72, 'it', '<h2>Lettera di Adesione</h2><p>Data: {date}</p><p>Caro/a <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>Siamo lieti di darti il benvenuto in {company_name} come {designation}.</p><p>Data di Inizio: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Stipendio: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Dipartimento: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>Non vediamo l\'ora del tuo prezioso contributo al successo della nostra azienda.</p><p>Cordiali saluti,<br><strong>Dipartimento HR</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(73, 'ja', '<h2>入社通知書</h2><p>日付: {date}</p><p><strong>{employee_name}</strong>様</p><p>{company_name}に{designation}としてご入社いただき、心より歓迎いたします。</p><p>入社日: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>給与: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>部署: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>弊社の成功への貴重な貢献を楽しみにしております。</p><p>敬具<br><strong>人事部</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(74, 'nl', '<h2>Toetredingsbrief</h2><p>Datum: {date}</p><p>Beste <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>We zijn verheugd u te verwelkomen bij {company_name} als {designation}.</p><p>Startdatum: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Salaris: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Afdeling: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>We kijken uit naar uw waardevolle bijdrage aan het succes van ons bedrijf.</p><p>Met vriendelijke groet,<br><strong>HR Afdeling</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(75, 'pl', '<h2>List Dołączenia</h2><p>Data: {date}</p><p>Drogi/a <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>Mamy przyjemność powitać Cię w {company_name} na stanowisku {designation}.</p><p>Data Rozpoczęcia: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Wynagrodzenie: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Dział: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>Czekamy na Twój cenny wkład w sukces naszej firmy.</p><p>Z poważaniem,<br><strong>Dział HR</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(76, 'pt', '<h2>Carta de Adesão</h2><p>Data: {date}</p><p>Caro/a <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>Temos o prazer de dar-lhe as boas-vindas à {company_name} como {designation}.</p><p>Data de Início: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Salário: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Departamento: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>Esperamos ansiosamente sua valiosa contribuição para o sucesso da nossa empresa.</p><p>Atenciosamente,<br><strong>Departamento de RH</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(77, 'pt-BR', '<h2>Carta de Adesão</h2><p>Data: {date}</p><p>Caro/a <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>Temos o prazer de dar-lhe as boas-vindas à {company_name} como {designation}.</p><p>Data de Início: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Salário: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Departamento: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>Esperamos ansiosamente sua valiosa contribuição para o sucesso da nossa empresa.</p><p>Atenciosamente,<br><strong>Departamento de RH</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(78, 'ru', '<h2>Письмо о Присоединении</h2><p>Дата: {date}</p><p>Уважаемый/ая <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>Мы рады приветствовать вас в {company_name} на должности {designation}.</p><p>Дата Начала Работы: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Зарплата: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Отдел: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>Мы с нетерпением ждем вашего ценного вклада в успех нашей компании.</p><p>С уважением,<br><strong>Отдел кадров</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(79, 'tr', '<h2>Katılım Mektubu</h2><p>Tarih: {date}</p><p>Sayın <strong>{employee_name}</strong>,</p><p>Sizi {company_name} şirketinde {designation} pozisyonunda karşılamaktan memnuniyet duyuyoruz.</p><p>İşe Başlama Tarihi: <strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>Maaş: <strong>{salary}</strong><br>Departman: <strong>{department}</strong></p><p>Şirketimizin başarısına değerli katkınızı dört gözle bekliyoruz.</p><p>Saygılarımızla,<br><strong>İnsan Kaynakları Departmanı</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17'),
(80, 'zh', '<h2>入职信</h2><p>日期：{date}</p><p>亲爱的<strong>{employee_name}</strong>，</p><p>我们很高兴欢迎您加入{company_name}，担任{designation}职位。</p><p>入职日期：<strong>{joining_date}</strong><br>薪资：<strong>{salary}</strong><br>部门：<strong>{department}</strong></p><p>我们期待您为公司成功做出宝贵贡献。</p><p>此致<br><strong>人力资源部</strong><br>{company_name}</p>', '[\"date\",\"company_name\",\"employee_name\",\"designation\",\"joining_date\",\"salary\",\"department\"]', 61, '2026-06-29 06:55:17', '2026-06-29 06:55:17');
INSERT INTO `landing_page_custom_pages` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `sections`, `show_breadcrumb`, `meta_title`, `meta_description`, `is_active`, `sort_order`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'About Us', 'about-us', '<h2>Empowering Businesses Through Smarter Workforce Management</h2><p>At <strong>dotHRM</strong>, we believe that people are the foundation of every successful organization. Managing employees, payroll, attendance, and workforce operations should be simple, efficient, and accessible—not time-consuming and complicated.</p><p>That\'s why we built <strong>dotHRM</strong>, a modern cloud-based Human Resource Management and Payroll platform designed to help businesses streamline HR operations, automate repetitive tasks, and create better workplace experiences.</p><p>Whether you\'re a startup managing your first employees, a growing business expanding your workforce, or an established organization looking to modernize HR processes, dotHRM provides the tools you need to manage your people with confidence.</p><hr><h2>Who We Are</h2><p>dotHRM is a technology-driven HR solutions platform dedicated to transforming how organizations manage their workforce. We combine powerful HR automation, payroll management, attendance tracking, leave administration, recruitment, and employee self-service capabilities into a single, easy-to-use platform.</p><p>Our goal is simple: help businesses spend less time on administrative work and more time focusing on growth, innovation, and employee success.</p><p>By leveraging modern cloud technologies and user-centric design, we deliver a solution that is scalable, secure, and built for the evolving needs of today\'s workplace.</p><hr><h2>Our Vision</h2><p>To become a leading HR technology platform that empowers organizations worldwide to build smarter, more productive, and people-centric workplaces.</p><hr><h2>Our Mission</h2><p>To simplify workforce management through innovative, reliable, and accessible software solutions that improve operational efficiency, enhance employee experiences, and support sustainable business growth.</p><hr><h2>What We Do</h2><p>dotHRM provides a complete suite of workforce management solutions designed to help organizations manage every stage of the employee lifecycle.</p><h3>Human Resource Management</h3><p>Centralize employee information, organizational structures, departments, designations, and workforce records in one secure location.</p><h3>Payroll Management</h3><p>Automate salary calculations, allowances, deductions, overtime, and payslip generation to ensure accurate and efficient payroll processing.</p><h3>Attendance &amp; Time Tracking</h3><p>Monitor employee attendance, shifts, overtime, and working hours while maintaining complete visibility across your organization.</p><h3>Leave Management</h3><p>Simplify leave requests, approvals, balances, and policies with automated workflows and real-time tracking.</p><h3>Recruitment &amp; Onboarding</h3><p>Streamline hiring processes from job posting and candidate evaluation to employee onboarding and integration.</p><h3>Performance Management</h3><p>Support employee growth through performance reviews, goal setting, feedback management, and workforce development initiatives.</p><h3>Reporting &amp; Analytics</h3><p>Access real-time workforce insights, HR reports, payroll summaries, attendance trends, and performance metrics to make informed decisions.</p><hr><h2>Why Businesses Choose dotHRM</h2><p>Organizations choose dotHRM because they need more than just software—they need a reliable partner that helps them manage their workforce effectively.</p><h3>Simplicity</h3><p>Our platform is designed to be intuitive and easy to use, reducing training time and improving adoption across teams.</p><h3>Automation</h3><p>Eliminate repetitive administrative tasks and focus on strategic HR initiatives that drive business value.</p><h3>Scalability</h3><p>Whether you have 10 employees or 10,000, dotHRM grows with your organization.</p><h3>Security</h3><p>We prioritize data protection through secure infrastructure, access controls, encryption, and industry best practices.</p><h3>Flexibility</h3><p>Customize workflows, departments, policies, and processes to align with your organization\'s unique requirements.</p><h3>Support</h3><p>Our team is committed to helping customers achieve success through responsive support and continuous platform improvements.</p><hr><h2>Our Core Values</h2><h3>Innovation</h3><p>We continuously explore new technologies and ideas to improve HR management and workforce productivity.</p><h3>Customer Success</h3><p>Our customers\' success drives every decision we make, from product development to support services.</p><h3>Reliability</h3><p>We build dependable solutions that organizations can trust for their daily HR operations.</p><h3>Transparency</h3><p>We believe in open communication, honest relationships, and clear business practices.</p><h3>Excellence</h3><p>We strive to deliver exceptional experiences through quality products, services, and support.</p><hr><h2>Our Commitment</h2><p>At dotHRM, we are committed to helping organizations navigate the future of work with confidence. As businesses evolve, workforce expectations change, and technology advances, we remain focused on delivering innovative HR solutions that empower organizations to succeed.</p><p>We understand that every employee matters, every process counts, and every organization deserves tools that simplify operations while supporting growth.</p><p>That\'s why we continue to invest in technology, innovation, and customer success to ensure dotHRM remains a trusted workforce management platform for businesses of all sizes.</p><hr><h2>Building the Future of HR</h2><p>The workplace is changing, and organizations need smarter tools to manage their most valuable asset—their people.</p><p>dotHRM is more than an HR software platform. It\'s a complete workforce management solution built to help businesses automate operations, improve employee engagement, enhance decision-making, and achieve sustainable growth.</p><p><strong>Join us in redefining HR management for the modern workplace.</strong></p><h3>dotHRM</h3><p><strong>Manage People. Simplify Payroll. Drive Growth.</strong> 🚀</p>', '[\"about\"]', 1, 'About Us - dotHRM Platform', 'Discover our dotHRM solution – a smart platform that simplifies payroll, attendance, recruitment, and performance management for businesses worldwide.', 1, 1, '2026-05-13 09:53:49', '2026-07-02 09:40:24'),
(2, 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy-policy', 'Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how our dotHRM software collects, uses, and safeguards your data.<br><b>Information We Collect:</b> &bull; Employee information such as name, contact details, and work profile &bull; Payroll and compensation details &bull; Attendance, leave records, and shift schedules &bull; Performance reviews, training data, and appraisals &bull; System usage analytics and activity logs<br><b>How We Use Your Information:</b> &bull; Provide, maintain, and improve dotHRM services &bull; Automate payroll processing, tax calculations, and compliance reports &bull; Track attendance, leaves, and performance efficiently &bull; Communicate important updates, policies, and notifications &bull; Ensure data accuracy, security, and compliance with labor laws<br><b>Information Sharing:</b> We do not sell or trade personal employee data. Information may be shared with: &bull; Authorized company administrators and HR managers &bull; Third-party service providers for operational purposes &bull; Legal authorities if required by law<br><b>Data Security:</b> We use encryption, access control, and audits to protect HR data from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure.<br><b>Data Retention:</b> Data is retained as long as required to fulfill policy purposes or as mandated by law; can be deleted or anonymized when no longer needed.<br><b>Your Rights:</b> You may access, update, or request deletion of personal data. Contact your employer or our support team for platform concerns.', NULL, 0, 'Privacy Policy - dotHRM', 'Read the privacy policy of our dotHRM platform to understand how employee and HR data is collected, used, and protected.', 1, 2, '2026-05-13 09:53:49', '2026-05-13 09:53:49'),
(3, 'Terms of Service', 'terms-of-service', 'Please read these terms carefully before using our dotHRM platform. By accessing or using our services, you agree to these terms.<br><br><b>Acceptance of Terms:</b> By creating an account or using our dotHRM product, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, you may not use the platform.<br><br><b>Service Description:</b> Our platform provides businesses with Human Resource Management solutions, including but not limited to:<br>&bull; Employee records and profile management<br>&bull; Attendance and leave tracking<br>&bull; Payroll and compensation management<br>&bull; Performance evaluation tools<br>&bull; Reports, analytics, and integrations<br><br><b>User Responsibilities:</b> As a user of our dotHRM, you agree to:<br>&bull; Provide accurate and updated information when creating an account<br>&bull; Maintain confidentiality of your login credentials<br>&bull; Ensure that all uploaded content complies with applicable laws<br>&bull; Use the platform only for lawful HR management purposes<br><br><b>Subscription & Payments:</b> You agree to pay all fees associated with your chosen plan in accordance with the billing terms. Failure to pay may result in suspension or termination of your account.<br><br><b>Termination of Service:</b> We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access if you violate these Terms or engage in harmful activities.<br><br><b>Data & Privacy:</b> Your data will be handled per our Privacy Policy. You are responsible for safeguarding your account access.<br><br><b>Limitation of Liability:</b> Our company shall not be held liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the dotHRM platform.', NULL, 0, 'Terms of Service - dotHRM', 'Read our terms of service to understand the rules and responsibilities for using our dotHRM platform.', 1, 3, '2026-05-13 09:53:49', '2026-05-13 09:53:49'),
(4, 'Contact Us', 'contact-us', 'Have questions about <b>dotHRM </b>? Our team is here to guide you every step of the way.<br><br><b>Send us a Message:</b> Fill out the form with your Full Name, Email Address, Subject, and Message. Our team will respond promptly.<br><br><b>Contact Information:</b><br>&bull; <b>Email Us:</b> support@hrm.com (Our team typically responds within 24 hours)<br>&bull; <b>Call Us:</b> +1 (555) 123-4567 (Available Monday – Friday, 9am – 6pm EST)<br>&bull; <b>Visit Us:</b> 123 Business Ave, Suite 100, San Francisco, CA 94105<br><br><b>Business Hours:</b><br>&bull; Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM EST<br>&bull; Saturday: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM EST<br>&bull; Sunday: Closed', '[\"contact\"]', 1, 'Contact Us - HRM Support', 'Get in touch with the HRM team for product support, questions, or partnership opportunities.', 1, 4, '2026-05-13 09:53:49', '2026-07-02 09:40:58'),
(5, 'FAQ', 'faq', 'Get quick answers to the most <b>common queries</b> about using our dotHRM platform.<br><br><b>Getting Started:</b><br><b>What is dotHRM?</b> Our dotHRM is an all-in-one platform to manage your employees, payroll, attendance, performance, and leave. It simplifies HR operations and helps businesses run efficiently.<br><b>How do I get started?</b> Follow these steps to set up your account:<br>&bull; Sign up for an dotHRM account<br>&bull; Set up your company profile and departments<br>&bull; Add employees and assign roles<br>&bull; Configure payroll, attendance, and leave policies<br>&bull; Start managing HR processes efficiently<br><br><b>Features & Plans:</b><br><b>Which plans are available?</b> We offer multiple subscription plans including Basic, Professional, and Enterprise, each with features tailored for businesses of all sizes.<br><b>Can I customize HR workflows?</b> Yes, you can customize workflows for attendance, leave approvals, performance reviews, and payroll according to your company policies.<br><br><b>Analytics & Support:</b><br><b>How can I monitor HR metrics?</b> Our analytics dashboard provides real-time insights on employee attendance, payroll reports, performance trends, and leave balances, helping you make informed HR decisions.', '[\"faq\"]', 1, 'FAQ - HRM Help Center', 'Find answers to frequently asked questions about dotHRM, including features, plans, employee management, and analytics.', 1, 5, '2026-05-13 09:53:49', '2026-07-03 04:52:49'),
(6, 'Refund Policy', 'refund-policy', 'We are committed to your satisfaction. Below is our refund policy, including eligibility, process, and exceptions.<br><br><b>30-Day Money Back Guarantee:</b> We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee for all premium plans. If you are not completely satisfied with dotHRM, we will refund your payment in full within 30 days of purchase.<br><br><b>Eligible Refunds:</b><br>- Monthly and annual subscription plans<br>- One-time premium features or add-ons<br>- Unused portions of prepaid services<br><br><b>Refund Process:</b><br>1. Contact our support team within 30 days of purchase<br>2. Provide your account details and the reason for the refund<br>3. We will review and process your request within 3–5 business days<br>4. Refunds will be issued to your original payment method<br><br><b>Non-Refundable Items:</b><br>- Custom development work or integrations<br>- Third-party services and add-ons<br>- Domain registration fees<br>- Services used after the 30-day guarantee period<br><br>If you have any questions regarding our refund policy, please contact our support team. We are happy to assist!', NULL, 0, 'Refund Policy - HRM', 'Learn about our refund policy and money-back guarantee for HRM services.', 1, 6, '2026-05-13 09:53:49', '2026-05-13 09:53:49'),
(7, 'Features', 'features', NULL, '[\"features\"]', 1, 'Features - dotHRM Platform', NULL, 1, 0, '2026-07-03 05:12:49', '2026-07-03 05:14:43'),
(8, 'Pricing', 'pricing', NULL, '[\"plans\"]', 1, 'Pricing - dotHRM Platform', NULL, 1, 0, '2026-07-03 05:15:45', '2026-07-03 05:16:01');
INSERT INTO `landing_page_settings` (`id`, `company_name`, `contact_email`, `contact_phone`, `contact_address`, `config_sections`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'dotHRM', 'support@dothrm.com', '+1 (555) 123-4567', 'Dubai Silicon Oasis, Dubai, UAE', '{\"sections\":[{\"key\":\"header\",\"transparent\":true,\"background_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"text_color\":\"#1f2937\",\"button_style\":\"gradient\"},{\"key\":\"hero\",\"title\":\"Smart HR & Payroll Software for ,Modern Businesses,\",\"subtitle\":\"Manage employees, payroll, attendance, leave, recruitment, and performance from a single cloud platform.\",\"announcement_text\":\"\\ud83d\\udce2 New: Smart Leave & Attendance Tracking Launched!\",\"primary_button_text\":\"Start Free Trial\",\"secondary_button_text\":\"Login\",\"image\":\"DTj2XB3XqTyRSiy5SAVJX6DJftz2xGTQnGDgmfgU.webp\",\"background_color\":\"#f8fafc\",\"text_color\":\"#1f2937\",\"layout\":\"image-right\",\"height\":600,\"stats\":[{\"value\":\"10K+\",\"label\":\"Active Users\"},{\"value\":\"50+\",\"label\":\"Countries\"},{\"value\":\"99%\",\"label\":\"Satisfaction\"}]},{\"key\":\"features\",\"title\":\"Everything Your ,HR Team, Needs\",\"description\":\"Stop managing employee records in spreadsheets and disconnected systems.<br>dotHRM provides a complete HR ecosystem that helps organizations streamline operations, improve productivity, and ensure compliance.\",\"background_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"layout\":\"grid\",\"columns\":3,\"image\":null,\"show_icons\":true,\"features_list\":[{\"title\":\"Employee Management\",\"description\":\"Maintain complete employee records in one centralized location.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Employee Profiles<\\/li>\\n<li>Document Management<\\/li>\\n<li>Departments & Designations<\\/li>\\n<li>Employee Lifecycle Tracking<\\/li>\\n<li>Organizational Structure<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"users\"},{\"title\":\"Payroll Management\",\"description\":\"Process salaries accurately and efficiently.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Payroll Generation<\\/li>\\n<li>Allowances & Deductions<\\/li>\\n<li>Overtime Calculations<\\/li>\\n<li>Payslip Generation<\\/li>\\n<li>Salary History<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"qr-code\"},{\"title\":\"Attendance Management\",\"description\":\"Track employee attendance with ease.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Daily Attendance<\\/li>\\n<li>Shift Management<\\/li>\\n<li>Late Arrival Tracking<\\/li>\\n<li>Overtime Management<\\/li>\\n<li>Attendance Reports<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"clock\"},{\"title\":\"Recruitment & Hiring\",\"description\":\"Manage hiring from application to onboarding.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Job Openings<\\/li>\\n<li>Applicant Tracking<\\/li>\\n<li>Interview Scheduling<\\/li>\\n<li>Candidate Evaluation<\\/li>\\n<li>Employee Onboarding<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"briefcase\"},{\"title\":\"Performance Management\",\"description\":\"Build a high-performing workforce.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Goal Management<\\/li>\\n<li>KPI Tracking<\\/li>\\n<li>Performance Reviews<\\/li>\\n<li>Employee Feedback<\\/li>\\n<li>Growth Planning<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"trending-up\"},{\"title\":\"Reports & Analytics\",\"description\":\"Gain visibility into your workforce.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Attendance Reports<\\/li>\\n<li>Payroll Reports<\\/li>\\n<li>Employee Insights<\\/li>\\n<li>Department Analysis<\\/li>\\n<li>Custom Reports<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"bar-chart\"},{\"title\":\"Employee Self-Service Portal\",\"description\":\"Give employees control over their information.\\nEmployees can:\\n<ul>\\n<li>View Payslips<\\/li>\\n<li>Apply for Leave<\\/li>\\n<li>Update Profile Information<\\/li>\\n<li>View Attendance Records<\\/li>\\n<li>Download Documents<\\/li>\\n<li>Access Company Announcements<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"user-check\"},{\"title\":\"Mobile Workforce Management\",\"description\":\"Manage HR operations anywhere.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Available on Mobile<\\/li>\\n<li>Attendance Check-In<\\/li>\\n<li>Leave Requests<\\/li>\\n<li>Employee Directory<\\/li>\\n<li>Payroll Access<\\/li>\\n<li>Notifications<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"smartphone\"},{\"title\":\"Security & Compliance\",\"description\":\"Your employee data is protected.\\n<ul>\\n<li>Enterprise-Grade Security<\\/li>\\n<li>Secure Cloud Infrastructure<\\/li>\\n<li>Data Encryption<\\/li>\\n<li>Role-Based Access Control<\\/li>\\n<li>Activity Logs<\\/li>\\n<li>Regular Backups<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"icon\":\"shield\"}]},{\"key\":\"screenshots\",\"title\":\"Ready to Transform Your ,HR Operations?,\",\"subtitle\":\"Automate HR processes, simplify payroll, and empower your workforce with dotHRM.\",\"screenshots_list\":[{\"src\":\"LJE7jqPbJvwAM95kawKqUzCeahkHq4RZovjjtfIX.webp\",\"alt\":\"HRM Dashboard Overview\",\"title\":\"Dashboard Overview\",\"description\":\"Get a complete overview of employee data, payroll, and HR activities in one unified dashboard.\"},{\"src\":\"QGkI6hm0jyFdf2ZHRrvV7pg5CHKYp7Fl3AZmixkE.webp\",\"alt\":\"Employee Management Module\",\"title\":\"Employee Management\",\"description\":\"Centralized employee profiles with personal details, documents, and job history.\"},{\"src\":\"KMlLctqXkfDxfp5YZFn1ZbAFff89eqWMaQYvFbP8.webp\",\"alt\":\"Payroll Automation\",\"title\":\"Payroll & Payslips\",\"description\":\"Automated payroll processing with tax calculations, allowances, and downloadable payslips.\"},{\"src\":\"dmaY6p8hT8zQXTwvPkU3iyYoVfxHcCBnmP97bQlS.webp\",\"alt\":\"Leave Management\",\"title\":\"Leave Management\",\"description\":\"Easily apply, approve, and track employee leave requests with proper workflows and policies.\"},{\"src\":\"zJsOTgti1KATwLOUAicscZD8zq0Rb52PKLwJ92uX.webp\",\"alt\":\"Attendance Tracking\",\"title\":\"Attendance Tracking\",\"description\":\"Monitor employee check-ins, check-outs, and shifts with automated attendance logs.\"},{\"src\":\"ICF4sOQ5fboJPaXoACYyaimxy2crr4OJohdVKhWU.webp\",\"alt\":\"Recruitment & Onboarding\",\"title\":\"Recruitment & Onboarding\",\"description\":\"Streamline hiring with applicant tracking and digital onboarding.\"}]},{\"key\":\"why_choose_us\",\"title\":\"Built for HR Teams. Designed for ,Impact.,\",\"subtitle\":\"dotHRM provides a complete HR ecosystem that helps organizations streamline operations, improve productivity, and ensure compliance.\",\"reasons\":[{\"title\":\"Save Time\",\"description\":\"Automate repetitive HR tasks and reduce administrative workload.\",\"icon\":\"clock\"},{\"title\":\"Improve Accuracy\",\"description\":\"Eliminate payroll errors and manual data entry mistakes.\",\"icon\":\"shield\"},{\"title\":\"Better Employee Experience\",\"description\":\"Empower employees through self-service tools and mobile access.\",\"icon\":\"heart\"},{\"title\":\"Real-Time Insights\",\"description\":\"Keep sensitive HR data safe with enterprise-grade security.\",\"icon\":\"bar-chart\"}],\"stats\":[{\"value\":\"10+\",\"label\":\"Integrated HR Modules\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"value\":\"100%\",\"label\":\"Cloud-Based Accessibility\",\"color\":\"green\"},{\"value\":\"98%\",\"label\":\"Customer Satisfaction\",\"color\":\"orange\"},{\"value\":\"Unlimited\",\"label\":\"Workforce Growth Potential\",\"color\":\"blue\"}],\"stats_title\":\"Everything Your HR Team Needs in One Platform\",\"cta_title\":null,\"cta_subtitle\":null},{\"key\":\"about\",\"title\":\"Powering Modern ,Workplaces,\",\"description\":\"Empowering Businesses Through Smarter Workforce Management\",\"story_title\":\"At dotHRM, we believe that managing people should be simple, efficient, and data-driven.\",\"story_content\":\"Our platform was created to help organizations move beyond spreadsheets, paperwork, and disconnected systems by providing a complete digital HR ecosystem.\\n\\ndotHRM combines Human Resource Management, Payroll Automation, Attendance Tracking, Recruitment, Employee Self-Service, and Reporting into a single cloud-based solution that helps businesses operate more efficiently and make better workforce decisions.\",\"image\":null,\"background_color\":\"#f9fafb\",\"layout\":\"image-right\",\"stats\":[{\"value\":\"100%\",\"label\":\"Innovation\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"value\":\"20+\",\"label\":\"Companies Served\",\"color\":\"green\"},{\"value\":\"8K+\",\"label\":\"Employees Managed\",\"color\":\"purple\"}],\"parallax\":true,\"values\":[{\"title\":\"Our Vision\",\"description\":\"To empower businesses with modern HR technology that drives efficiency, growth, and workforce excellence.\",\"icon\":\"lightbulb\"},{\"title\":\"Our Mission\",\"description\":\"To simplify HR and payroll management through intelligent, user-friendly software that enhances productivity and employee experiences.\",\"icon\":\"zap\"},{\"title\":\"Our Values\",\"description\":\"We are committed to innovation, reliability, transparency, and customer success in everything we build.\",\"icon\":\"award\"},{\"title\":\"Our Promise\",\"description\":\"To deliver secure, scalable, and easy-to-use HR solutions that help organizations manage their people with confidence.\",\"icon\":\"star\"}]},{\"key\":\"team\",\"title\":\"Meet Our Team\",\"subtitle\":\"We\'re a dedicated team of HR and technology experts.\",\"cta_title\":\"Want to Join Our Team?\",\"cta_description\":\"We\'re always looking for talented individuals to shape the future of HR management.\",\"cta_button_text\":\"View Open Positions\",\"members\":[{\"name\":\"John Doe\",\"role\":\"CEO & Founder\",\"bio\":\"Experienced HR tech entrepreneur passionate about building intuitive HR solutions.\",\"image\":null,\"linkedin\":\"#\",\"email\":\"john@example.com\"},{\"name\":\"Jane Smith\",\"role\":\"CTO\",\"bio\":\"Leads the tech team to create scalable and secure HR platforms.\",\"image\":null,\"linkedin\":\"#\",\"email\":\"jane@example.com\"},{\"name\":\"Michael Lee\",\"role\":\"Head of Product\",\"bio\":\"Designs user-centric features to simplify HR processes.\",\"image\":null,\"linkedin\":\"#\",\"email\":\"michael@example.com\"},{\"name\":\"Emily Davis\",\"role\":\"HR Manager\",\"bio\":\"Oversees employee engagement, recruitment, and HR operations.\",\"image\":null,\"linkedin\":\"#\",\"email\":\"emily@example.com\"}]},{\"key\":\"testimonials\",\"title\":\"What Our ,Clients, Say\",\"subtitle\":\"Hear from HR leaders who trust our platform.\",\"trust_title\":\"Trusted by HR Professionals Worldwide\",\"trust_stats\":[{\"value\":\"4.9\\/5\",\"label\":\"Average Rating\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"value\":\"500+\",\"label\":\"Companies Served\",\"color\":\"green\"}],\"testimonials\":[{\"name\":\"Alice Johnson\",\"role\":\"HR Manager\",\"company\":\"GlobalTech Ltd.\",\"content\":\"HRM has made managing employee records and attendance effortless. Our HR team saves hours every week!\",\"rating\":5},{\"name\":\"Robert Smith\",\"role\":\"Operations Head\",\"company\":\"Innovate Solutions\",\"content\":\"The payroll automation is incredibly accurate and easy to use. No more manual calculations or errors!\",\"rating\":5},{\"name\":\"Maria Davis\",\"role\":\"CEO\",\"company\":\"BrightFuture Corp.\",\"content\":\"From recruitment to performance management, HRM covers everything we need in one platform.\",\"rating\":5},{\"name\":\"David Lee\",\"role\":\"Talent Acquisition Lead\",\"company\":\"NextGen Enterprises\",\"content\":\"Recruitment and onboarding have never been smoother. HRM platform is intuitive and efficient.\",\"rating\":5},{\"name\":\"Samantha Green\",\"role\":\"Payroll Specialist\",\"company\":\"BrightSolutions Inc.\",\"content\":\"Payroll processing is now quick and error-free thanks to HRM. It has transformed our monthly workflow.\",\"rating\":5},{\"name\":\"Michael Brown\",\"role\":\"HR Coordinator\",\"company\":\"TechWave Ltd.\",\"content\":\"The performance management module helps us track employee goals and progress effortlessly.\",\"rating\":5}]},{\"key\":\"plans\",\"title\":\"Choose Your ,dotHRM Plan,\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with our free plan and upgrade as your team grows.\",\"faq_text\":\"Have questions about our plans? Reach out to our sales team for guidance.\"},{\"key\":\"faq\",\"title\":\"Everything You Need to ,Know,\",\"subtitle\":\"Got questions? We\'ve got answers.\",\"cta_text\":\"Still have questions?\",\"button_text\":\"Contact Support\",\"faqs\":[{\"question\":\"What is dotHRM?\",\"answer\":\"dotHRM is a cloud-based HR and Payroll Management platform that helps businesses manage employees, attendance, leave, payroll, and workforce operations from a single system.\"},{\"question\":\"Who is dotHRM designed for?\",\"answer\":\"dotHRM is built for startups, SMEs, enterprises, educational institutions, healthcare providers, and organizations looking to streamline HR processes.\"},{\"question\":\"Does dotHRM support payroll processing?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. dotHRM automates salary calculations, allowances, deductions, overtime, and payslip generation to simplify payroll management.\"},{\"question\":\"Can employees access their own HR information?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Employees can view payslips, check attendance records, submit leave requests, update profiles, and access company information through the self-service portal.\"},{\"question\":\"Is dotHRM accessible from anywhere?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. As a cloud-based solution, dotHRM can be accessed securely from any device with an internet connection.\"},{\"question\":\"How secure is employee data in dotHRM?\",\"answer\":\"Security is a top priority. dotHRM uses secure authentication, role-based access controls, data encryption, and regular backups to protect sensitive information.\"},{\"question\":\"Can dotHRM be customized for my organization?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. dotHRM can be configured to match your company structure, departments, payroll policies, leave rules, and approval workflows.\"},{\"question\":\"How do I get started with dotHRM?\",\"answer\":\"Simply request a demo or contact our team. We\'ll help you set up your organization, onboard employees, and get started quickly.\"}]},{\"key\":\"newsletter\",\"title\":\"Stay ,Updated, with dotHRM\",\"subtitle\":\"Get the latest updates, HR tips, and feature announcements.\",\"privacy_text\":\"No spam, unsubscribe at any time.\",\"benefits\":[{\"icon\":\"\\ud83d\\udce7\",\"title\":\"Weekly Updates\",\"description\":\"Stay informed about the latest dotHRM features and improvements.\"},{\"icon\":\"\\ud83d\\udca1\",\"title\":\"HR Insights\",\"description\":\"Get tips and best practices to optimize your HR operations.\"},{\"icon\":\"\\ud83d\\udcca\",\"title\":\"Reports & Trends\",\"description\":\"Receive analytics insights and industry trends directly to your inbox.\"}]},{\"key\":\"contact\",\"title\":\"We\'re Just a ,Message Away,\",\"subtitle\":\"Have questions about dotHRM? Our team is here to help you discover how smarter HR and payroll management can transform your business.\",\"form_title\":\"Send Us a Message\",\"info_title\":\"Contact Information\",\"info_description\":\"Whether you\'re looking for a product demo, pricing information, technical support, or partnership opportunities, we\'d love to hear from you.\",\"layout\":\"split\",\"background_color\":\"#f9fafb\",\"faqs\":[{\"question\":\"Can I request a live demo of dotHRM?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Our team can schedule a personalized demo to showcase the platform and answer your questions.\"},{\"question\":\"How quickly will I receive a response?\",\"answer\":\"We typically respond to all inquiries within 24 business hours.\"},{\"question\":\"Do you provide onboarding and support?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. We offer onboarding assistance, training, and ongoing support to help you get the most out of dotHRM.\"}]},{\"key\":\"footer\",\"description\":\"dotHRM is a cloud-based HR and Payroll software that helps businesses manage employees, attendance, leave, payroll, recruitment, and workforce operations from one platform.\",\"newsletter_title\":\"Stay Updated\",\"newsletter_subtitle\":\"Get HR insights, payroll tips, and dotHRM product updates.\",\"links\":{\"product\":[{\"name\":\"Features\",\"href\":\"#features\"},{\"name\":\"Pricing\",\"href\":\"#pricing\"}],\"company\":[{\"name\":\"About Us\",\"href\":\"#about\"},{\"name\":\"Contact\",\"href\":\"#contact\"}],\"support\":[{\"name\":\"Help Center\",\"href\":\"#help-center\"},{\"name\":\"FAQ\",\"href\":\"#faq\"},{\"name\":\"Refund Policy\",\"href\":\"#refund-policy\"}],\"legal\":[{\"name\":\"Terms of Service\",\"href\":\"#terms\"},{\"name\":\"Privacy Policy\",\"href\":\"#privacy\"}]},\"social_links\":[{\"name\":\"Facebook\",\"icon\":\"Facebook\",\"href\":\"#\"},{\"name\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"Twitter\",\"href\":\"#\"},{\"name\":\"LinkedIn\",\"icon\":\"Linkedin\",\"href\":\"#\"}],\"section_titles\":{\"product\":\"Product\",\"company\":\"Company\"}}],\"theme\":{\"primary_color\":\"#3b82f6\",\"secondary_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"accent_color\":\"#f7f7f7\",\"logo_light\":null,\"logo_dark\":null,\"favicon\":null},\"seo\":{\"meta_title\":\"dotHRM - Smart HR & Payroll Software for Modern Businesses\",\"meta_description\":\"Manage employees, payroll, attendance, leave, recruitment, and performance from a single cloud platform.\",\"meta_keywords\":\"HR software, HRM, employee management, payroll, attendance tracking, recruitment, performance management\"},\"section_order\":[\"header\",\"hero\",\"features\",\"screenshots\",\"why_choose_us\",\"about\",\"team\",\"testimonials\",\"plans\",\"faq\",\"newsletter\",\"contact\",\"footer\"],\"section_visibility\":{\"header\":true,\"hero\":true,\"features\":true,\"screenshots\":true,\"why_choose_us\":true,\"about\":true,\"team\":false,\"testimonials\":true,\"plans\":true,\"faq\":true,\"newsletter\":true,\"contact\":true,\"footer\":true}}', '2026-05-13 09:53:59', '2026-07-02 11:43:55');
